        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER You hoist up a bucket of water.
        ECHO OTHERS %N hauls a bucket of water up the well chute.
        ECHO ALL A youngster clips an empty bucket on the well line after %n hauls up some water.
        NEWITEM 7 1960
ENDIF
