REGION 20
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
You climb the mountain's steep side through dense woods composed of oak, maple,
and pine, the latter's sharp clean scent making you breathe deeply in appre-
ciation. The air is cool here beneath the trees, the sunlight dimmed by thick
foliage overhead. You can hear the wind brushing lightly through the branches
above, and from far aloft the scream of a hunting hawk drifts down to your
ears.
*DESCRIPTION_END
